.PP 
.SS "panel::backend::CurrentWindowXorgImpl::CurrentWindowXorgImpl (QObject * parent = \fRnullptr\fP)\fR [explicit]\fP"

.PP
Constructs the XOrg/X11 implementation for active window tracking\&. 
.PP
\fBParameters\fP
.RS 4
\fIparent\fP (QObject*) The parent QObject\&.
.RE
.PP
Connects to the X display, selects \fRPropertyChangeMask\fP on the root window so that \fR_NET_ACTIVE_WINDOW\fP changes are delivered, then sets up a \fRQSocketNotifier\fP on the XCB file descriptor to receive those events without blocking the Qt event loop\&. Finally, reads the initial active window\&. 
.PP
\fBReturns\fP
.RS 4
void 
.RE
.PP

